trans-unit.source: Allows activity designer developers to add custom designer verb providers to an activity designer.
trans-unit.target: Kan aktiviteten designer utviklere Legg til egendefinert designer verbet leverandører Aktivitetsdesigner en.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Classes that implement this interface can add and remove custom verb providers--any classes that implement the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider> interface -- to and from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> classes.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Klasser som implementerer dette grensesnittet kan legge til og fjerne egendefinerte verbet leverandører--klasser som implementerer den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider>grensesnittet--til og fra <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>klasser.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider>

trans-unit.source: Adds a class that implements the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider"></xref> interface to the list of verb providers that an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> uses.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en klasse som implementerer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider"> </xref> grensesnittet i listen over verb leverandører som en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> bruker.

trans-unit.source: Removes a class that implements the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider"></xref> interface to the list of verb providers that an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> uses.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner en klasse som implementerer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider"> </xref> grensesnittet i listen over verb leverandører som en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> bruker.

trans-unit.source: VerbProviders returns an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider> collection that contains all verb providers associated with a specific <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: VerbProviders returnerer en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider>samling som inneholder alle verb-leverandører som er knyttet til en bestemt <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerVerbProvider>
